  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Geisha Clan, Level 8+ <br />Your bodyguard has trained like no other to protect you. Whether to further his skills or protect your life, he is above many other bodyguards.<br />Your bodyguard gains the following:</p><ul><li>If he is within half of his movement speed from you, he can use his reaction to reach you and take the damage for you.</li><li>Your bodyguard gains an additional 2 ASI points that you can distribute wherever you wish.</li><li>Your bodyguard's AC increases by 1 and his movement speed increases by 10 feet.</li><li>Your bodyguard can, once per day, survive a mortal blow, going to 1 HP instead of 0.</li><li>Share Pain: The bodyguard can use an action at the start of combat. As long as you are close to your bodyguard (up to 30 ft), every damage the Geisha takes will be halved, and the reduced amount will be transferred to the bodyguard. This damage cannot be reduced in any way, the Bodyguard must be in combat with the Geisha for this to work.</li><li>Your bodyguard's basic attack (Heavy Punch, Slash and Stab, Chakra Bolt, Illusory Attack) gains the Multiattack trait.</li></ul>",
      "chat": ""
    },
